 ******************************
**     **Game Notes:**        **
 ****************************** 

 After the battle is over, someone has to cleanup the mess! Introducing Viscera
 Cleanup Detail: Shadow Warrior from RuneStorm, a unique crossover mini-game that
 combines the worlds of Viscera Cleanup Detail and Shadow Warrior. Step into the
 rubber soled shoes of the hapless janitor tasked with cleaning up Lo Wang's mess
 after a devastating katana battle in the collector's temple from Shadow Warrior.
 Mop up pools of blood, dispose of body parts, and get the collector's gallery of
 antiques in tip top shape as quick as possible! Successfully clean the entire 
 temple and collect all the scattered cash to unlock two Steam achievements!


 *****************************

 ***************************** 
 
 1. Unpack release
 2. Install 
 3. Copy over the cracked content from the /Crack dir to your main game dir
 4. Play!
